Class 2

@FindBy another technique/approach to locate elements. It uses all available locators in Selenium:
id
name
className
tagName
linkText
partialLinkText
xpath
css

Syntax for FindBy

@FindBy (locator="locatorValue") 
access modifier WebElement nameOfElement

US24548: Add Employee Details

TestCase: Add Employee Verification
Step 1: Login to the OrangeHRM
Step 2: Click on PIM
Step 3: Click on Add Employee
Step 4: Enter fName, lName, select Location
Step 5 Click Save
Step 6: Verify employee is added

Lets say your script failed and it says 
NoSuchElementException unable to locate element with id='txtUserName'
